<%- include("partials/header") %>

<section class="legend-page legend-heaven">
  <div class="container legend-shell">
    <div class="legend-grid">
      <div class="legend-poster-wrap heaven-glow">
        <div class="legend-poster">
          <div class="legend-coming-soon">Coming Soon</div>
          <div class="legend-placeholder">
            <div class="legend-placeholder-box">
              <div class="legend-placeholder-text">Josiah Image Placeholder</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="legend-copy">
        <div class="legend-badges">
          <span class="legend-badge heaven">Heaven</span>
          <span class="legend-tier">Destiny-Bound</span>
        </div>

        <h1>Josiah</h1>
        <p class="legend-role">The Child of Prophecy</p>
        <p class="legend-lead">
          Josiah is the living collision point between prophecy, bloodline, and supernatural war.
          After the sky breaks open, his life becomes a trigger point for powers that have waited across ages.
        </p>

        <div class="legend-actions">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/">Return Home</a>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/characters/set">View Set</a>
        </div>

        <div class="legend-panels">
          <div class="legend-panel">
            <h2>Description</h2>
            <p>
              He is not merely part of the prophecy. He is one of the reasons it moves.
              His survival is tied to an ancient conflict stretching across Heaven, Earth, and the unseen realm.
            </p>

            <div class="legend-power-grid">
              <div class="legend-power-card"><h3>Destiny Link</h3><p>Bound to world-shifting prophecy.</p></div>
              <div class="legend-power-card"><h3>Awakening</h3><p>His identity unfolds as war rises.</p></div>
              <div class="legend-power-card"><h3>Bloodline</h3><p>Connected to powers older than nations.</p></div>
              <div class="legend-power-card"><h3>Survival</h3><p>Remains central under impossible pressure.</p></div>
            </div>

            <div class="legend-quote">“He is not just in the prophecy. He is one of its keys.”</div>
          </div>

          <div class="legend-panel">
            <h2>Profile</h2>
            <div class="legend-profile">
              <div class="legend-row"><span class="legend-label">Faction</span><span class="legend-value">Heaven</span></div>
              <div class="legend-row"><span class="legend-label">Role</span><span class="legend-value">The Child of Prophecy</span></div>
              <div class="legend-row"><span class="legend-label">Power Theme</span><span class="legend-value">Destiny / Awakening / War</span></div>
              <div class="legend-row"><span class="legend-label">Visual</span><span class="legend-value">Image Coming Soon</span></div>
              <div class="legend-row"><span class="legend-label">Background</span><span class="legend-value">Placeholder Active</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include("partials/footer") %>